                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-247-18690111 t18690111-247-punishment-84"></join>Eighteen Months' Imprisonment each</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY</hi>, 1st <hi rend="smallCaps">FEBRUARY</hi>, 1869.</p>
